Fix service worker registration to not use module type

Removes { type: 'module' } from the service worker registration call.
Using module type causes the browser to not send cookies with service
worker requests, resulting in 401 authentication errors.

Index: code-editor-src/src/vs/workbench/contrib/webview/browser/pre/index.html
